Erik Per Sullivan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erik_Per_Sullivan 0 Erik Per Sullivan (born July 12, 1991) is a former American actor. He is best known for his role as Dewey, the younger brother to middle child Malcolm, on the Fox series Malcolm in the Middle, which was on air for seven years.
